### System Info API Tests
### Tests for SystemInfoController endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080
### OpenCode server: http://localhost:4096

### Get system health status
### Returns health status of the OpenCode server
GET http://localhost:8080/api/system/health
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get available skills
### Returns list of available AI skills/capabilities
GET http://localhost:8080/api/system/skills
Content-Type: application/json

###
